title: Laundry Facilities, Spacious Layouts, Two Playgrounds
posting_body: ['The Woodmark', '2425 South 96th Street , Tacoma, WA, 98444', 'Want more info on this unit?', 'See the link (below):', '<URL>', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 22', 'OR Text', '22', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to text us.', 'Affordable Living in Tacoma', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 950 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'We are temporarily ceasing in-person tours with prospective residents.', 'Virtual tours are available.', 'Call us today for more information!', 'Discover affordable housing that doesn’t sacrifice quality or convenience when you rent an apartment at The Woodmark in Tacoma, WA.', 'The spacious one and two bedroom homes available pair comfortable interior features and exciting amenities with a location you’ll love.', 'Learn more today.', 'Features', '- Balcony or Patio', '- Large Closets', '- Full Size Washers & Dryers*', '- Spacious Layouts', '- Equipped Kitchens', 'Community Amenities', '- Ample Parking', '- Seasonal Swimming Pool', '- Laundry Facilities', '- Beautiful Park-Like Setting', '- Two Playgrounds', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Saturday:10:00AM-5:00PM', 'Pet Policy', 'We welcome 2 pets per apartment home.', 'There is a $300 deposit and a $250 non-refundable fee per pet.', 'Pet rent is $20 per pet per month.', 'Breed restrictions apply.', 'We do not accept Comprehensive Reusable Tenant Screening Reports as defined by and pursuant to RCW 59.18.', '51r1cV0NYmz']
